verbose_text: Puerarin attenuated the DEX induced release of cytochrome c and cleavage of caspase-3, and treatment with puerarin inhibited the c-Jun N-terminal kinase (JNK) pathway and activated the phosphoinositide 3-kinase (PI3K)/Akt pathway in the hFOB1.19 cells.
evidence: Puerarin attenuated the DEX-induced release of cytochrome c
